---
description: CareSutra project rules
alwaysApply: true
---

This project is CareSutra.

CareSutra is an Indian personal service brand for insurance, loans, and alternative health services.

Use:
- Next.js App Router
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- shadcn/ui
- Prisma
- MySQL database: caresutra_db

Git repo:
https://github.com/manishmk1980/caresutra

Do not reference:
www.kreatorbox.com/caresutra

Brand rules:
- Do not redesign the logo.
- Use existing CareSutra logo from public/images/brand/.
- Tone should be trustworthy, simple, supportive, and Indian audience friendly.
- Use clean blue/gold-inspired palette.
- Avoid clutter and over-animation.

SEO rules:
- Every public page must have metadata.
- Use semantic HTML.
- Use only one H1 per page.
- Add Open Graph metadata.
- Keep public content indexable.

Development rules:
- Do not hardcode secrets.
- Use .env and .env.example.
- Keep components modular.
- Keep Phase 1 simple but scalable.
